\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
The Pythagoreans were a philosophic guild that took the great Greek mathematicia
n Pythagoras's teachings as the basis for a philosophical system.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Legend has it that Hippasus, a follower of Pythagoras, discovered a proof
